                <p><lb n="1"/>rājagirinivāsikasa<lb n="2"/>vetikānavakamikasa<lb n="3"/>therāsa bhayatabudharakhitasa<lb n="4"/>At<unclear>e</unclear>vāsi<supplied reason="lost">niya</supplied> <unclear>Ā</unclear>rikaya bhikhun<unclear>i</unclear>na budhar<unclear>a</unclear>khita<unclear>ya</unclear><lb n="5"/>sadhutuka<supplied reason="lost">ya</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>yadhamadinaya sagharakhi<lb n="6" break="no"/>tasa ca dānaṁ
                </p>
