            <div type="translation">
                <p>Gift of the noble <supplied reason="explanation" cert="low">ārikā</supplied> nun <persName>Buddharakkhitā</persName>—pupil of the elder, reverend <persName>Buddharakkhita</persName>, the resident of <placeName>Rājagiri</placeName> and superintendent of construction of the <supplied reason="subaudible">Great Shrine’s</supplied> railing <supplied reason="explanation">vedikānavakammika</supplied>—together with her daughter, the noble <persName>Dhammadinnā</persName>, and of <persName>Saṅgharakkhita</persName>.</p>
            </div>
